glosses: to kill, to murder (with accusative case)

examples.translation: Kill flies before typhoid fever kills you.

examples.text: Boş zamanlarını çok fazla bilgisayar oyunları oynayarak öldürme.
examples.translation: Don't waste your free time with playing computer games too much.

etymology: Causative form of ölmek (“to die”). Ultimately from Proto-Turkic *öltür- (“to kill”)
